twitch_info.title: CN3 F100 grind day ?? + 1
twitch_info.description: Hi it's been a while since I bothered streaming this, but I've been nibbling at it behind the scenes and I'm ready to get back to it. My skills have improved quite a bit in orange and green room, I'm actually getting to blue every now and then. Sadly I learned buckethead can mute my streams so as much as I love the song, I'm going go with the roulette of whatever music I decide to put on. This time it was Neon White OST.
